author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
First of all - before watching this, please visit: 
https://youtu.be/S_MijiGiQNI?si=0CWyaLs11B5rpSr9
to see "In The Name of The Father" in its entirety. The thinking computer objected to our inclusion of the whole track on copyright grounds, so apologies for the short clips.   The single is the first from President - whose name first appeared on the Download Festival's lineup. The identity of who is behind the mask was not initially revealed and my question to you is, does it really matter?

To see more from JHRA,  join my Patreon here: http://www.patreon.com/jushawk

For Cameo messages: https://www.cameo.com/justinhawkins

The new Darkness album "Dreams On Toast" is available now: https://thedarkness.lnk.to/dreamsontoast/

title: Does Anyone Not Know Who President Is?
